name: Chat-sys
tagline: Full fledged Chat system leveraging on Ajax and PHP richness
body:
### Welcome to KevBar Chat System.
Was inspired by the trending world of online communities

### Designer Templates
We’ve crafted some handsome templates for you to use. Go ahead and click 'Continue to layouts' to browse through them. You can easily go back to edit your page before publishing. After publishing your page, you can revisit the page generator and switch to another theme. Your Page content will be preserved.


### Authors and Contributors
Authored and Maintained by:Kevin Barasa (@bqevin).

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with Pages? Check out our [documentation]or [contact support](https://github.com/bqevin) and we’ll help you sort it out.
